kgmoji\" /> <br />\n用人地車好喇<br />\n快得果0.幾秒"},{"pid":"9d7a3b680ead5e89059b54d63d7e421a7d677887","tid":472042,"uid":70135,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"入咩波都問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好揸出街害人啦"},{"pid":"cf5eb2cc96d4aa2e6acf785c43b2df4631c5bf65","tid":472042,"uid":8963,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔踩盡極力子轉波會唔會傷車 <br />\n上次去芬蘭考賽車牌啲老師咁教 話轉波會快啲</blockquote><br />\n咁係因為你落場個時間要快就所有嘢都要快，而且好多外國人有一架track car 專係落場用所以佢哋唔會錫車<br />\n而你平時架腳車係咪落場專用先？如果係咁你咪做。但如果你個架只係腳車，咁點解要做一樣加快你個極力子收皮嘅事？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 你連依啲揸棍波一定會識嘅簡單常識都唔知就唔好考賽車牌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324afcb268d0ff42062a10b638a19af517a8340f","tid":472042,"uid":123497,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:06:50.000Z","msg":"用波控速<br />\n緊急時用brake<br />\n所以好多野要plan定<br />\n唔係就好蝕brake皮"},{"pid":"f864cfb8dfb8e4d847ccd7bc686885b549bf8b88","tid":472042,"uid":19431,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入咩波都問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好揸出街害人啦</blockquote><br />\n學緊車問有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識咪問囉<br />\n總好過考完個牌出到街先出事先黎問呀"},{"pid":"021e1ac1bcc2be892f436c344d7919b08388cab1","tid":472042,"uid":9608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T10:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>問多一題<br />\n<br />\n請問考試結束，空波，熄匙後，究竟係入一波定入R波, 阿sir教我入阿R波, 亦已經習慣入R波。<br />\n<br />\n但又見到有人話係入一波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n考天光道， 結束位置係平路</blockquote><br />\n幾年前考天光道 熄車後一波pass<br />\n你問清楚師傅好</blockquote><br />\n睇個官咩心情嫁<br />\n我師傅都係教返試場熄匙入一波<br />\n但我考果日  個官一路除安全帶一路同我講<br />\n下次熄匙入返R波<br />\n我果下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打定輸數咁入office 拎成績<br />\n丫屌  佢又反高潮比左個牌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上次考車 一停車個考官就沖左落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連我入咩波都無睇到<br />\n最後pass左</blockquote><br />\n入咩波都得</blockquote><br />\n咩波都得架啦 要個engine lock住架車渣嗎 姐係好似自動波p波咁"},{"pid":"b87704c0683b6975795ab13982dfa5abe74418db","tid":472042,"uid":15186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T11:13:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入咩波都問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好揸出街害人啦</blockquote><br />\n學緊車問有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識咪問囉<br />\n總好過考完個牌出到街先出事先黎問呀</blockquote><br />\n召喚lihkg所有學神/P牌巴絲 (13)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/447827/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/447827/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9bc277272ae3038205f70565dc5daba326b4c96b","tid":472042,"uid":138834,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T11:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用波控速<br />\n緊急時用brake<br />\n所以好多野要plan定<br />\n唔係就好蝕brake皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n波箱貴定brake皮貴<br />\n有得用brake一定brake行先"},{"pid":"5bc11e996d8f315942c29ab56ee1df640c70597b","tid":472042,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T11:24:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入咩波都問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好揸出街害人啦</blockquote><br />\n學緊車問有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識咪問囉<br />\n總好過考完個牌出到街先出事先黎問呀</blockquote><br />\n咩車任何時段都可以空波<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n渣緊車一定唔會問呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n考車果陣大大個item 空波滑行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我渣棍仔會入空波溜車 慢慢溜到燈位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自動波唔會  一鬆油門就溜車 唔會轉空波<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電車就一鬆電門就扯停架車咁 都係溜"},{"pid":"9b6070a8acb61bd8255e6af95c45ce3403989bad","tid":472042,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T11:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用波控速<br />\n緊急時用brake<br />\n所以好多野要plan定<br />\n唔係就好蝕brake皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n波箱貴定brake皮貴<br />\n有得用brake一定brake行先</blockquote><br />\n大車呢一定係拖低波架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係一失靈就出事炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e19e7b7849f66c9e4f6f71d9364eaaec1b542e","tid":472042,"uid":57584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T09:47:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae7f51be042cc0a4ad6ee0f442a8c278cb3b4136","tid":472042,"uid":57584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T09:48:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c09068f8dbf2f6cdc6b90be7bd60e40984bac68","tid":472042,"uid":6221,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T10:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用波控速<br />\n緊急時用brake<br />\n所以好多野要plan定<br />\n唔係就好蝕brake皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n波箱貴定brake皮貴<br />\n有得用brake一定brake行先</blockquote><br />\n呢啲concept害死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通你落長斜入空波只用brake? <br />\n如果你brake fluid overheat的話會無哂效能<br />\n車頭整咁大個冷排就係用黎absorb engine+transmission heat"},{"pid":"d5e152c87d9d671dbaebfe94d4171128df952dbf","tid":472042,"uid":15647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T10:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用波控速<br />\n緊急時用brake<br />\n所以好多野要plan定<br />\n唔係就好蝕brake皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n波箱貴定brake皮貴<br />\n有得用brake一定brake行先</blockquote><br />\n大車呢一定係拖低波架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係一失靈就出事炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢條命應該平過波箱"},{"pid":"6f6eede6ef8ce63b6c9fc131ef268e5cae99f88f","tid":472042,"uid":134711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:45:39.000Z","msg":"其實睇車速，車負重。如果私家車，唔係 full load, 大直平路，前面有燈位，我會空波溜去燈位。<br />\n<br />\n如果車速快，會入低波拖慢。命仔貴過 brake, gear box, clutch"},{"pid":"0459e073b3204bbd32e85e5ddfdaf807601d4174","tid":472042,"uid":134711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:47:30.000Z","msg":"不過新牌仔就唔好學。操熟正確程序先，即係用低波拖慢架車"},{"pid":"e2e694dc71756f33fb62454ea36a1e6e2e9f6f06","tid":472042,"uid":134711,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T11:53:27.000Z","msg":"仲有，即使係轉低波，我唔會4波落3波再落2波先停車空波。<br />\n<br />\n停車，開車，行車都係。要睇情況。<br />\n<br />\n例如，用二波上完斜，如果變左落斜，我可能會跳去四波，架車夠力就得。<br />\n<br />\n以上係自己的做法。冇人教，不知是否正確 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf8e155e6201aab8d8738b9838f19e52b3d2256","tid":472042,"uid":3399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:38:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有，即使係轉低波，我唔會4波落3波再落2波先停車空波。<br />\n<br />\n停車，開車，行車都係。要睇情況。<br />\n<br />\n例如，用二波上完斜，如果變左落斜，我可能會跳去四波，架車夠力就得。<br />\n<br />\n以上係自己的做法。冇人教，不知是否正確 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔通你4波拖落2波咁西利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾高轉數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉數再大啲好似會入唔到波"},{"pid":"831a748f7fbe6d73f27d8942cd0b1540724c367e","tid":472042,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T05:15:06.000Z","msg":"落斜一定要空波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cb45703e56a6acd6fca163c78f4556d3238ddb","tid":472042,"uid":136589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T05:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果行緊車想3波轉4波<br />\n唔小心入左後波架車會點<br />\n雖然應該唔會有人咁白痴<br />\n但想知有咩後果</blockquote><br />\nyoutube 有鬼佬試過行160 入後波，架車睬你鳩傻一路直去冇慢過"}]}